        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4091020763" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5226050790911142123">This is a very touching book. I read it in Vietnamese but since I’m not used to writing reviews in my own language, I used English instead. At first, I’m a bit confused when Oscar depicted his age so fast. Then, I started to understand. It’s very sad that Oscar, who had cancer, died in the end. I found it pretty great, entering a young boy’s mind in a children’s hospital, playing with ladies in pink, trading candies with friends,… Oscar said that he loved it there. In this book, we found Oscar o</span>
  <span id="freeText5226050790911142123" style="display:none">This is a very touching book. I read it in Vietnamese but since I’m not used to writing reviews in my own language, I used English instead. At first, I’m a bit confused when Oscar depicted his age so fast. Then, I started to understand. It’s very sad that Oscar, who had cancer, died in the end. I found it pretty great, entering a young boy’s mind in a children’s hospital, playing with ladies in pink, trading candies with friends,… Oscar said that he loved it there. In this book, we found Oscar overhearing his parents talk to the doctor, hiding in the broom cupboard or whatever and hating them, falling asleep. Here, we experienced what Oscar did for his last ten days. In an overview, I’m glad Oscar lived to his fullest life. It’s just so sad that he passed away, I cried a bit there…</span>
  <a data-text-id="5226050790911142123" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


